Y'all!!!!!! Our production intern, Jack Cook is starting today! He comes to us from Stanford where he studied Symbolic Systems with a focus in Computer Music, and is interested, in his words in "the grey space between science and the arts." I think he'll fit in well. :) 

He'll be sitting by Lynsey and Evans in the south room (390), and we'll be at Walnut with :bagelbounce: DONUTS :bagelbounce: at 10:30! Come say hi!
